cc:Work.dc:title: Flower Multi-Choice Template
cc:Work.dc:description: Flower template with multi-choice possibilities. Ten layers. Nine sizes. Eighty petals in all. Combine various layers to make various flowers and various sizes. One layer makes a daisy. Many layers make a carnation or mum. Cut and fold petals for different effects. Color flowers by your choice.Experiment to see what you can create.
